1509213.title: Central Park West - 61st Street - 62nd Street

718438f-a.folder: Central Park West & 61st Street, Manhattan, NY
718438f-a.text:
The Mayflower Apartment Hotel, Central Park West, west side, from 6lst to 62nd Streets. At the extreme right may be seen a portion of the Century Theatre.
1927.
Joseph Smith.
718438f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 61st Street

718439f-a.folder: Central Park West & 61st Street, Manhattan, NY
718439f-a.text:
Central Park West, west side, from 6lst to 63rd Streets, showing in centre Century Theatre (1909-1930). At left is Mayflower Hotel; at right is Society for Ethical Culture.
May 25, 1928.
P.L. Sperr, Photographer.

The same, showing in centre clearing on former site of Century Theatre where Century Apartments will be erected.
January 23, 1931.
P.L. Sperr, Photographer.
